<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Habibi Restaurant</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,600;1,500&family=Jost:wght@300;500&display=swap');
:root{--ink:#1a120b;--terra:#c2592f;--gold:#cc9a4a;--gold2:#e0c388;--cream:#f3e9d6;--cream2:#cdbfa5}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{min-height:100vh;
background:linear-gradient(rgba(26,18,11,.88),rgba(26,18,11,.93)),url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555939594-58d7cb561ad1?w=1600&q=70') center/cover fixed,var(--ink);
font-family:'Jost',sans-serif;color:var(--cream);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:48px 24px}
.eyebrow{font-size:12px;letter-spacing:6px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold2);animation:fadeUp .6s ease both}
h1{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:600;font-size:clamp(36px,7vw,60px);margin:24px 0 10px;animation:fadeUp .6s ease .1s both}
h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--gold)}
p{color:var(--cream2);max-width:420px;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:34px;animation:fadeUp .6s ease .2s both}
.ticket{width:100%;max-width:440px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#2c1d12,#20140d);border:1px solid rgba(204,154,74,.3);
border-radius:4px;padding:26px;position:relative;box-shadow:0 30px 60px -25px rgba(0,0,0,.8);
animation:fadeUp .6s ease .3s both;transition:box-shadow .3s,transform .3s}
.ticket:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 35px 70px -25px rgba(0,0,0,.9),0 0 0 1px rgba(204,154,74,.25)}
.ticket::before{content:"";position:absolute;top:-7px;left:0;right:0;height:14px;
background:radial-gradient(circle,var(--ink) 5px,transparent 5.5px) repeat-x;background-size:22px 14px}
form{display:flex;gap:10px}
input{flex:1;background:rgba(243,233,214,.05);border:1px solid rgba(204,154,74,.35);border-radius:3px;
padding:13px 16px;color:var(--cream);font-family:inherit;font-size:15px;outline:none;transition:.25s}
input:focus{border-color:var(--gold);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(204,154,74,.18)}
button{font-size:13px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink);
background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--gold2),var(--gold));border:none;border-radius:3px;padding:0 22px;cursor:pointer;transition:.2s}
button:hover{filter:brightness(1.1);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.or{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;width:100%;max-width:300px;margin:32px 0 24px;color:var(--cream2);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;animation:fadeUp .6s ease .4s both}
.or span:not(.txt){flex:1;height:1px;background:rgba(243,233,214,.15)}
.menu-link{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:22px;font-weight:600;color:var(--terra);
text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid #8f3f22;padding-bottom:4px;transition:.25s;animation:fadeUp .6s ease .5s both;display:inline-block}
.menu-link:hover{color:var(--gold);border-color:var(--gold);transform:translateX(4px)}
a[href*="addItem"]{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:var(--gold2);
text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(204,154,74,.4);padding-bottom:3px;transition:.25s;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:16px}
a[href*="addItem"]:hover{color:var(--gold);border-color:var(--gold);transform:translateX(4px)}
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@media(max-width:480px){form{flex-direction:column}body{background-attachment:scroll}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<span class="eyebrow">LB Kitchen &amp; Grill</span>
<h1>Welcome to <em>Habibi</em> Restaurant</h1>
<p>Open-flame grills, slow spice blends, and family recipes — served the old way.</p>

<div class="ticket">
  <form action="/search" method="GET">
    <input type="text" name="q" placeholder="Search the menu..." required>
    <button type="submit">Search</button>
  </form>
</div>

<div class="or"><span></span><span class="txt">or</span><span></span></div>

<a href="http://localhost:3000/addItem">Add Items</a>
<a class="menu-link" href="http://localhost:3000/getMenu">View the full menu →</a>
</body>
</html>